 web of history, gain a new interest.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aEnglish fictiony19th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aFictionxTechnique. 0aNarration (Rhetoric)xHistoryy19th century. 0aRealism in literature. 0aReality in literature. 4aEngland. 4aLiterary Studies. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / English, Irish, Scottish, Welsh.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Backlist 2000-2013z978311053615740uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150171821240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501718212423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501718212/original  a978-3-11-053615-7  Cornell University Press Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles